    public class HwMMUImpl
extends HwStorageManagerImpl
implements HwMMU
    An implementation of the model object 'Hw MMU'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Virtual Addr Space
    • Physical Addr Space
    • Memory Protection
    • Nb Entries
    • Owned TL Bs
